         MACRO                                                          00160000
.*                                                                      00170000
.* Load and Test Characters into a register                             00180000
.*                                                                      00190000
&LABEL   LTC   &REG,                   * Register to load              *00200000
               &LOC,                   * Location of character         *00210000
               &MASK                   * Mask for ICM (default=NNNY)    00220000
.*                                                                      00230000
.* &REG  specifies the register to load                                 00240000
.* &LOC  specifies the location of the character(s) to be loaded        00250000
.* &MASK specifies which bytes of the register are to be loaded         00260000
.*                                                                      00270000
